{"tid":397388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網購滅蟲煙霧彈 18歲仔險屋都燒毀","createTime":"2017-09-12T12:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T13:01:08.000Z","uid":80761,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea3e10941fd37ee662849ce20269f51fe5dcd43","tid":397388,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"【17：14更新】新增影片<br />\n荃灣大河道57號1樓一劏房單位，中午12時許發生火警，冒出大量濃煙，其他住客發現，通知保安員報警。消防接報破門入屋，發現涉事劏房的房間內無人，瞬即把火救熄，調查後懷疑有人在房間內放置滅蟲劑後離開，火種燒着雜物引起火警，事件中沒有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n涉事劏房單位一劏二，男戶主姓尹，任職裝修工，與妻子及18歲就讀IVE的次子居於上址約7年，其20餘歲的長子早已搬出居住。尹表示，由於近日天雨後劏房多蝨子和曱甴，其次子疑早前經網購滅蟲煙霧彈，並燃點放在房間內驅蟲。現場一張睡床燒毀尤其嚴重，疑滅蟲煙霧彈放在床下底，燒着雜物一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n事發時屋內無人，業主其後通知尹返回單位，他直言過往已叮囑兒子不要胡亂網購，無奈今次發生火警，唯有稍後進行裝修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170912&amp;guid=57200532&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170912%26guid%3D57200532%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=8bPRNTdYQG2t6jThgla6w2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e93c15f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170912%26guid%3D57200532%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=e9ff8990\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170912&amp;guid=57200532&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>IVE仔</strong></span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5053aa340f4757cb90ffc1a693606bd7a243047d","tid":397388,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"696ace7f558ae54dd21f4547b4f0956cc514b0bc","tid":397388,"uid":112355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"火攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma